Introduction: - Reference No. Mahatma Jotirao Phule Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti has been established under section 1. The committee was reconstituted under Reference H.C. and the term of the committee was extended by three years. The government was considering extending the term of the committee by appointing new invitees to the committee.
Government Decision: - The Government Decision dated 8th January, 2022 of the Mahatma Jotirao Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti has been reconstituted as follows.

para_trans: 2. Dr. Hari Narke's name is being dropped from the committee as he has passed away.
In addition to the above-mentioned invited members, the following dignitaries, who are biographers of Mahatma Jotirao Phule, are being newly appointed as invited members on the said Committee.
The term of the said Committee shall be till 30th June, 2024.
